### 🚨 BOTTLENECK #3: Evolution Engine Bounded Memory Growth

**Severity:** 🟠 High | **Impact:** Memory leak on long-running OpenClaw sessions

**Evidence — `src/self-evolution.ts`:**

```typescript
// Line 162: evolutionHistory — unbounded array, never trimmed
private evolutionHistory: EvolutionResult[] = [];  // ← grows forever

// Line 168: backups — set but only deleted on SUCCESSFUL rollback
private backups: Map<string, Backup> = new Map();  // ← one per skill, overwritten on re-evolve
// BUT: if evolveSkill() fires repeatedly (auto-trigger), each new backup overwrites.
// If rollback fails (line 380), old backup is NOT deleted — leak per failed attempt.

// Line 166: appliedCandidates — deleted only after VERIFICATION_COUNT (20) traces
private appliedCandidates: Map<string, AppliedCandidate> = new Map();
// If traces aren't recorded frequently (e.g., low-activity session), entries persist indefinitely.
// Each AppliedCandidate holds: content (string) + metadata ≈ 500 bytes–2KB per entry.

// Line 156: pendingEvaluations — cleaned up correctly (finally block), but Map is keyed by
// `${skill.slug}:${index}:${content.substring(0, 50)}` which creates many unique keys during
// bulk evolution (10 candidates × N skills = many keys per session)
```

**Code location:** `src/self-evolution.ts:155–170`, `src/self-evolution.ts:358–385`

**Recommended fix — add bounded storage with FIFO eviction:**

```typescript
// Replace unbounded arrays/maps with bounded versions

private evolutionHistory: EvolutionResult[] = [];
private readonly MAX_EVO_HISTORY = 100; // Keep last 100 evolutions

private backups: Map<string, Backup> = new Map();
private readonly MAX_BACKUPS = 20;      // Max 20 skill backups

private appliedCandidates: Map<string, AppliedCandidate> = new Map();
private readonly MAX_APPLIED = 20;      // Max 20 in-flight verifications

// Helper: bounded insert with FIFO eviction
private boundedInsert<K, V>(map: Map<K, V>, key: K, value: V, maxSize: number): void {
  if (map.size >= maxSize && !map.has(key)) {
    // Delete oldest entry (first key in iteration order)
    const firstKey = map.keys().next().value;
    if (firstKey !== undefined) map.delete(firstKey);
  }
  map.set(key, value);
}

// In evolveSkill() or commitEvolution():
this.boundedInsert(this.backups, skillSlug, backup, this.MAX_BACKUPS);
this.boundedInsert(this.appliedCandidates, skillSlug, applied, this.MAX_APPLIED);
this.evolutionHistory.push(result);
if (this.evolutionHistory.length > this.MAX_EVO_HISTORY) {
  this.evolutionHistory.shift();
}
```

**Expected improvement:** Memory growth bounded from O(evolution events × skill count) to O(1) with fixed max ~2MB. Eliminates long-tail memory leak.

